  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study the effect of Duodenal jejunal bypass on human adults with type 2 diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Adults non obese ( BMI less than 34 ) will undergo duodenal jejunal bypass. The Outcome
      measures: Blood Sugar, Insulin,HbA1c, CCK,Gastrin, GIP1and 2, Ghrelin, Cholesterol,
      Triglycerides,FFA, C-Peptide.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
